    "This study provides theoretical supplementation to manifesting the Retrocue Effect in educational settings.",
    "It strengthens the Cognitive Theory of Multimedia Learning (CTML) with specific pedagogical strategies by combining it with SR. From a practical perspective, the current research synthesizes current findings and can serve as a valuable reference for educators and researchers in this field.",
    "As with any systematic review, the current research has limitations inherent to the selection and filtering process.",
    "Primarily, the sample size is restricted to articles available through the Web of Science, IEEE, and Scopus databases.",
    "There might be relevant and high-qualify studies published outside these three databases and are worthy studying."
